title: Check Out Scenes From The First 2016 Dem Debate
text: The Democrats running for president face off for the first time Tuesday at a debate in Las Vegas. The debate, hosted by CNN, will feature former Secretary of State Hillary Clinton, Sen. Bernie Sanders (I-Vt.), former Sen. Jim Webb (D-Va.), former Rhode Island Gov. Lincoln Chafee and former Maryland Gov. Martin O'Malley.
